                <h1>Can Wallpaper Stick to Textured Walls?</h1>
                <p>Wallpaper can adhere to textured walls, but success depends on the texture's depth and type. Smooth textured surfaces work best, while very rough or heavily textured walls may present challenges. Using a strong adhesive, and ensuring the wallpaper is properly installed, can help achieve a more even finish.</p>
